meplay to the next dimension.- The game become really fun to play after you are passed the long learning curve.- The evenly matched online games are awesome to play and even give a satisfied feeling if are defeated.- When played accordingly the mechanics and synergy systems implemented are brilliant.- This game offers you a very broad selection of units. There are unlimited combinations to combine into a deck.Summary: At the beginning really hard to play and a long learning curve ahead. But after a long time and alot of patience, the game is really rewarding at the moment of battle and afterwards at the scoreboard.I recommend this game to players who have the time AND the will to learn how the game works."
