ife military equipment and outfits.Community is toxic. Much worse than the World of Tanks community from my experience.Tl:Dr: Best RTS ever with the same hard af learning curve. Good for beginners because all RTS'es are hard to learn either way and might as well pick up a S tier RTS. Extreme challenge with extreme rewards.10/10PS: Dark Souls of RTS games?"
