oes x (after that ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥t) and then reloactes his frontal armor to y, because 1500m away (and thats no joke) is a cheap transport thats just standing the open - making himself extremly vulnerable to the Tank-hunter at x. I lost already way too much high value units because of that♥♥♥♥♥♥and there is not a single way to disable this ""feature"". And dont fool yourself. This dosent happen once every 50 matches, but *every single match you will ever play*. All of these problems. It just kills all of the potential fun, desicion making and overall gameplay.Just spam, micro and abuse silly mechanics to win the day.Dont bother and buy yourself something that you will actually enjoy."
