76561197970773588,Recommended,251060,26584371,"Posted: 13 November, 2016",all,Milo.[HUN],"Wargame is the best modern military RTS out there, period.You can go from satellite view to unit level view without a hitch and the graphics don't disappoint. Beautiful landscape, models and animations, nice soundscape (from radio chatter to explosions) and a realistic combined arms gameplay.It has a steep learning curve - due to realistic unit movement speeds, you need to think two steps ahead, and not only manage the usual build-move-attack trio, but also manage your supply lines. You can have the best units out there on the front without your supply trucks replenishing their ammo or fuel.Unfortunatly, the AI cheats at anything above Easy level (more reinforcements than it should have), so it's not easy to learn and progress on your own. I'm told multiplayer is the real meat of the game - I've yet to try anything beyond coop vs AI with a friend.If you're interested in modern military tech and battlefield tactics, this is a must buy for you."
